high_descs: Turn right and face the stove.
Pick up the kettle from the front left burner.
Turn left and face the cabinet below the counter.
Open the cabinet door, place the kettle inside of the cabinet, close the door.
Turn right to face the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the kettle from the counter.
Turn left to face the cabinet below the counter.
Open the cabinet door, place the kettle to the left of the first kettle inside the cabinet, and close the door.
anns.task_desc: To move two kettles to the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn to the right to face the stove.
Pick up the tea pot from the left side.
Hold the tea pot and turn to the left.
Open the bottom cabinet and place the tea pot inside. Shut the door.
Turn to the right, to face the stove.
Pick up the tea pot from the counter on the left side.
Hold the tea pot and turn to the left.
Open the bottom cabinet and place the tea pot inside. Shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Move two tea pots to a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn right towards the stove.
Pick up the tea pot on the left front burner on the stove.
Turn left then face the counter top
Place the tea pot inside, then close the door.
Turn right towards the stove, then pick up the tea pot located on the right of counter top
Turn left then face the counter top
Open the cabinet door underneath the counter top on the left side.
Place the tea pot inside the cabinet next to the other one then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place two tea pots underneath the cabinet.
